<h1>Stay in touch with loved ones</h1>
<h2>4 free photo cards from TouchNote</h2>
<div class="status hint-text-gift"> <p>Gift</p> </div>
<div class="offer-info">
<p> TouchNote is all about the real sharing of precious moments, to help you keep close when you’re apart, whether you &amp; yours are in Manchester, Miami or Mexico City. With free worldwide delivery, TouchNote help you stay connected with personalised photo cards as special as they are. </p>
<p> This exclusive offer lets you enjoy your first 4 photo cards free as part of a 14-day trial. Simply follow the link to set up your account and in seconds you’re ready to create your first card. Then it's time to snap a pic or choose from any of your photos, add your message and click send - it’s that easy. </p>
<p> <b>To take advantage of this exclusive offer:</b> </p>
<p> 1. Click below to redeem and visit the TouchNote site </p>
<p> 2. Create your account </p>
<p> 3. You can then start to create your first card. After your first card is created, you’ll be invited to join one of TouchNote's membership plans </p>
<p> 4. Please make a choice and choose your preferred payment method (no payment will be taken until the 14-day trial and 4 card offer has passed. After this point payment will be taken automatically). If you choose not to proceed you will not be enrolled in the free trial and no cards will be sent </p>
<p> 5. Once enrolled in the free 14-day trial, your first card is complete and confirmed </p>
<p> 6. You’re now free to create and send your remaining 3 free cards </p>
<p> <b>If you do not wish to take a paid membership you can cancel any time in the 14-day period and any cards created up to that point will still be sent. After 14-days your chosen plan and preferred payment method is activated and the first payment is taken.</b> </p>
<p> Remember you can always view your redemption history <a href="/my-rewards" target="_blank">here</a>. </p>
