<h2>The legal bit</h2>
<p>By joining the trial, the first 4 cards are free and can be sent within 14 days.     </p>
<p><b>A customer, upon signing up, can either choose to take up a membership plan or click the “x”. If a membership plan is chosen, the customer will be asked to enter their payment details and payment for the membership will be taken automatically at the end of the free trial, unless cancelled. If you choose not to proceed you will not be enrolled in the free trial and no cards will be sent</b>.</p>
<p>A customer can cancel anytime during the trial to avoid being charged. Membership will auto-renew unless cancelled. Automatic renewal of a membership can be cancelled at any time.     </p>
<p>All membership fees are non-refundable after purchase.     </p>
<p>By signing up for a free trial, a customer agrees to TouchNote’s <a href="https://touchnote.com/policy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://touchnote.com/terms" target="_blank">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>.    </p>
